Summary: Approximately 9:30pm 3 orange spheres traveling east to west and then accended. Followed by a single light at 9:38pm doing the same thing.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was out at approximately 9:30pm on June 16th, 2012 walking my dogs when I observed 3 orange objects traveling east to west in the sky above me for approximately 2 to 3 minutes before they assended upward going out of view. I was able to get my girlfriend out to view the last minute or so of the event. At 9:38pm the exact same event happened with a single object traveling the same path and then accending out of view. Some poor quality video was obtained of the second event which I can send upon request.
